Subject: [PATCH] Merge In Field/Pre Delivery and Approved vs Unapproved into
 one page

- Combine the two Tickets dashboards into a single in-field-pre-delivery.html
  with three anchored sections: Created by Month, Approved, Unapproved.
- Sticky segmented tab bar + smooth scroll; sidebar buttons jump to
  #created and #approved respectively.
- Hardcode SAP report baseline (Jan 2025 - May 2026) for created/approved/
  unapproved; merge live dashboard values from June 2026 onward
  (claimCreatedMonthly + approvalClosedMonthly).
- Shared year/range filter and KPI summary across all three sections.
- Update index.html nav links; remove approved-unapproved.html.

